</td></tr></table><table><tr><td></td><td colspan='3'><b>Hours Worked</b> <i>shown in the following color (if any)&nbsp;</i></td><td style='background-color:#99FF33; border:1px solid #7ACC29;'></td><td colspan='4'><i>&nbsp;indicates that the employee has worked for more than </i><b>8 hours</b>.,</td><td style='background-color:red; border:1px solid red;'></td><td colspan='4'><i>Gatepass expired </i>.</td></tr></table>